- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper presents a controller for multirotor swarms, which falls under the domain of robotics. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper proposes a decentralized stable controller for close-proximity flight, which is a control problem. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper uses a Deep Neural Network to learn the high-order multi-vehicle interactions, which is a machine learning technique. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper uses a Deep Neural Network to learn the high-order multi-vehicle interactions, which is a subfield of AI. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition): Although not the main focus of the paper, computer vision techniques may be used for swarm sensing and perception, which is relevant to this work.
